&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;नारायणसूक्तम् 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
