        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Narayan Suktam 
    &lt;div id=&#34;narayan-suktam&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#narayan-suktam&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;audio controls&gt;
  &lt;source src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/036-narayanSuktam.mp3&#34; type=&#34;audio/mp3&#34;&gt;
  Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio&gt;     
&lt;p&gt;सहस्रशीर्षं देवं विश्वाक्षं विश्वशम्भुवम् । &lt;br&gt;
विश्वं नारायणं देवं अक्षरं परमं पदम् ।&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;विश्वतः परमान्नित्यं विश्वं नारायणग्ं हरिम् । &lt;br&gt;
विश्वं एवेदं पुरुषस्तद्विश्वं उपजीवति ।&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;पतिं विश्वस्यात्मेश्वरग्ं शाश्वतग्ं शिवमच्युतम् । &lt;br&gt;
नारायणं महाज्ञेयं विश्वात्मानं परायणम् ।&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
